high_descs: Turn around, then turn to face the table to your right.
Pick up the lettuce in front of the tomato on the table.
Turn to the right, walk forward to face the sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink beside the knife, turn on the water, turn of the water.
Pick up the lettuce out of the sink, turn around, cross the room and face the refrigerator to your left.
Open the refrigerator, place the lettuce in the refrigerator behind the apple, close the door.
anns.task_desc: Rinse the lettuce and place it inside the refrigerator.

high_descs: Turn around, go forward a step, turn right to face the wood table.
Take the lettuce from the table.
Turn right, go forward to the sink, move left to face the counter to the left of the sink.
Was the lettuce in the sink, take the lettuce from the sink.
Turn around, go straight to the wall, turn left, go straight to the fridge.
Put the lettuce behind the apple in the fridge.
anns.task_desc: Put washed lettuce in a fridge.

high_descs: Move to stand in front of the table with all the food on it.
Pick up the head of lettuce from the table.
Carry the head of lettuce to the kitchen sink.
Place the lettuce in the sink, fill with water, and then remove the lettuce once it is washed.
Carry the lettuce to the fridge.
Open the fridge and place the lettuce on the top shelf on the right side.
anns.task_desc: Place washed lettuce in the fridge.
